Name: mypy_extensions
URL: https://github.com/python/mypy_extensions
Revision: 70d9435779df27a522b146f2c5dee06ccacae373
License: MIT License
License File: src/LICENSE
Description: mypy_extensions is Python standard library typing module supported by the mypy
type checker and the mypyc compiler.
Revision is from `git merge-base JIRI_HEAD origin/upstream/release-1.1.0`.
Local Modifications: Added __init__.py to ensure the directory is treated as a Python package,
enabling proper imports.
Upgrading the version of mypy_extensions: Run `integration/third_party/pylibs/update-pylibs.sh` script to automatically
figure out the right version for mypy_extensions package based on the version
of the mypy.
